{"tid":729903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[人類總是] 又有個傻仔唔見左野","createTime":"2018-07-05T03:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T06:33:04.000Z","uid":111949,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed6dca438eef6c108fd110950c3b1a1bf56218c","tid":729903,"uid":111949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:09:35.000Z","msg":"其實唔見左野果個係我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係一個深藍色卡套<br />\n入面有八達通同其他member卡<br />\n估計應該係琴晚係680巴士上面唔見左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係我蠢 係我白痴 係我唔小心冇放好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知都應該幾難搵得番<br />\n但係個卡套係人地送<br />\n好有紀念價值<br />\n希望連登有愛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為表誠意 附上J圖數張<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/110534_6627982d1b0046284017124f14a111fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F110534_6627982d1b0046284017124f14a111fe.jpg&h=4948d43c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/110534_27cb26b24b9d96997ddfd2c4d2207015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F110534_27cb26b24b9d96997ddfd2c4d2207015.jpg&h=da6cd799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/110534_f1581f7082611d6e0fc8df2a67e29861.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F110534_f1581f7082611d6e0fc8df2a67e29861.jpg&h=58f19acf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cb97081a94f52c86d1068688f7aaec083ae0b73","tid":729903,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T03:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/